() Tj
T*
(PURPOSE) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This policy update introduces revised operating, leave, and compliance rules for Acme) Tj
T*
(Corporation. These updates supersede any conflicting provisions in prior policy documents.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. WORK MODEL AND ATTENDANCE \(UPDATED\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(? Standard work week remains Monday to Friday.) Tj
T*
(? Employees must be available during core collaboration hours: 10:00 AM to 3:00 PM local time.) Tj
T*
(? Eligible employees may work remotely up to 4 days per week with manager approval.) Tj
T*
(? Team attendance day is mandatory every Wednesday for hybrid teams.) Tj
T*
(? Timesheet submission deadline is now end of day Friday each week.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2. LEAVE POLICY \(UPDATED\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2.1 ANNUAL LEAVE) Tj
T*
(? Full-time employees receive 22 paid annual leave days per calendar year.) Tj
T*
(? Annual leave accrual is monthly from date of joining.) Tj
T*
(? Up to 12 unused annual leave days can be carried forward.) Tj
T*
(? Leave requests of 3 or more consecutive days must be submitted at least 7 calendar days in) Tj
T*
(advance.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2.2 SICK LEAVE) Tj
T*
(? Employees receive 14 paid sick leave days annually.) Tj
T*
(? Medical documentation is required for sick leave longer than 2 consecutive work days.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2.3 WELLNESS DAY) Tj
T*
(? Employees receive 2 paid wellness days per year.) Tj
T*
(? Wellness days do not carry forward to the next calendar year.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3. INFORMATION SECURITY AND AI USAGE \(NEW\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(? Multi-factor authentication is mandatory for all company systems.) Tj
T*
ET
