(4. HR OPERATIONS AND COMPLIANCE \(UPDATED\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(? Mandatory compliance training must be completed within 15 days of assignment.) Tj
T*
(? Managers must complete probation review checkpoints at day 30, day 60, and day 90.) Tj
T*
(? Internal transfer requests require a minimum of 9 months in current role unless CHRO) Tj
T*
(exception is approved.) Tj
T*
(? All policy violations are triaged by HR within 2 business days.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5. EXPENSE AND REIMBURSEMENT \(UPDATED\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(? Expense claims must be submitted within 7 business days of expense date.) Tj
T*
(? Claims above USD 500 require manager pre-approval reference.) Tj
T*
(? Missing receipts above USD 25 require a signed declaration form.) Tj
T*
(? Reimbursements are processed in the next payroll cycle after approval.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
